# ============================================================
# AICompanyManager DB Exact Design
# ============================================================

app_name: AICompanyManager
display_name: AI企業運営アプリ
category: 03.business-app
phase: Phase B
status: db-exact-design-fixed

## 1. Purpose

本書は AICompanyManager の BusinessOS 側 DB exact design を定義する。

本書は設計書であり、DB適用はまだ行わない。
実DDL適用は Phase C 以降で、DB担当レビュー後に行う。

## 2. Schema

canonical_schema: business

理由:
- AICompanyManager は business-app である
- 人間の事業運用、承認、納品、履歴を持つ
- AI社員実体は AIWorkerOS 側に置く
- AIWorkerOS の内部 pipeline 正本は複製しない

## 3. Table List

| table | purpose |
|---|---|
| business.ai_company_manager_company | AI企業の運用単位 |
| business.ai_company_manager_project | 事業案件 |
| business.ai_company_manager_policy | 人間が入力した方針 |
| business.ai_company_manager_pipeline_run | AIWorkerOS pipeline 実行単位の app-side tracking |
| business.ai_company_manager_role_assignment | President / Manager / Leader / Worker の割当表示 |
| business.ai_company_manager_stage | pipeline stage tracking |
| business.ai_company_manager_deliverable | 成果物管理 |
| business.ai_company_manager_review | レビュー結果 |
| business.ai_company_manager_return_request | 差し戻し |
| business.ai_company_manager_approval | 人間承認 |
| business.ai_company_manager_delivery | 納品 |
| business.ai_company_manager_queue_item | app-side local queue meaning |
| business.ai_company_manager_audit_log | 操作・状態変更・承認の監査ログ |

## 4. Table Exact Design

### 4.1 business.ai_company_manager_company

Purpose:
AI企業運営単位を管理する。

Columns:

| column | type | required | note |
|---|---|---:|---|
| company_id | uuid | yes | primary key |
| owner_user_id | uuid | yes | app user |
| company_name | text | yes | AI企業名 |
| display_name | text | no | 表示名 |
| description | text | no | 説明 |
| status | text | yes | active / paused / archived |
| aiworker_org_ref | text | no | AIWorkerOS 側組織参照 |
| created_at | timestamptz | yes | 作成日時 |
| updated_at | timestamptz | yes | 更新日時 |

### 4.2 business.ai_company_manager_project

Purpose:
人間が依頼する事業案件を管理する。

Columns:

| column | type | required | note |
|---|---|---:|---|
| project_id | uuid | yes | primary key |
| company_id | uuid | yes | company reference |
| owner_user_id | uuid | yes | app user |
| project_title | text | yes | 案件名 |
| project_summary | text | no | 案件概要 |
| project_status | text | yes | pipeline status enum |
| priority | text | yes | low / normal / high / urgent |
| due_at | timestamptz | no | 希望期限 |
| delivery_format | text | no | markdown / document / spreadsheet / code / other |
| human_approval_required | boolean | yes | default true |
| current_pipeline_run_id | uuid | no | current run |
| created_at | timestamptz | yes | 作成日時 |
| updated_at | timestamptz | yes | 更新日時 |

